steps.name: closed popup of last transaction details if open
I select "From" and "To" destination with next corresponding Date
Select "class" and booking "time" at 10 am for "AC 3 Tier (3A)" or 11 am for "Sleeper"
I click on search and select correct "train number"
As per Class selection select refresh, get the vacancy count
validate if vacancy count is more than or equal to 1 in case of single member and vacancy count is more than or equal to 5 in case of family booking
if count is less then 1 in case of single member or less than or equal to 5 in case of family then click on next available date
click on corresponding book now button and if any popup displayed click on yes and proceed further
fill individual or family Passenger Details such as Name,age, gender, India as country and preference as No preference for
Select Payment option as bhim pay
validate if vacancy count is still more than 0
Popup with Captcha to fill by user
Click continue and then select "BHIM/ UPI/ USSD" and click "Pay using BHIM (Powered by PAYTM ) also accepts UPI" and clcik "Pay and Book"
